OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWarnings as UK swimming    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpool closures revealed     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Swimmers across the UK have lost access
OL,6, to more than 60 public pools in the    
OL,7, last three years, BBC News has found.  
OL,9,FFreedom of Information requests to UK  
OL,10,Fcouncils revealed 65 pools had closed, 
OL,11,Feither temporarily or permanently, in  
OL,12,Fthe three years to March 2022.         
OL,14,FUkactive said a lack of staff, rising  
OL,15,Fenergy costs and chemical shortages had
OL,16,Fcreated a "perfect storm" for centres. 
OL,18,FGreg Whyte, a board member at the      
OL,19,Forganisation, said the closures were an
OL,20,F"absolute health and welfare disaster".
